premise_source_doc_sentence: In 2008 , T.I. received two wins from 11 nominations , including Most Performed Song for `` My Love '' at the ASCAP Pop Music Awards .
Wallace received two nominations from the Billboard Music Awards in 1995 , including Rap Artist of the Year and Rap Single of the Year .
In 2004 , he received two wins from six nominations , including Best Street Anthem for `` Rubberband Man '' at the Vibe Awards .

Pawlenty was rumored to be a contender for both the Republican presidential and vice presidential nominations during the 2008 election , and he officially sought the 2012 Republican presidential nomination from May to August 2011 .
